reviewText: Excellent Set

SENSATIONAL, SUPERB, MAGNIFICO, STUPENDOUS, FANTASTIC, and its good too; all five seasons!!  From Amazon I got mine.!!  Five Stars.

When we received the pack there were a few loose discs but it was due to the type of DVD package. There were a couple scratches but everything worked great. We were able to binge watch with no problems. Love this show and can't wait till the next season!!
